# =============================================================================
# A/B TESTING NOTES
# =============================================================================

# The multi-prompt A/B testing framework uses:
# - prompts.yaml for configuration management
# - Google Sheets for comparative data collection  
# - Sequential processing for rate limit safety
# - Prompt version tracking for systematic optimization
#
# Edit prompts.yaml to:
# - Add new prompt variations
# - Enable/disable prompts with active: true/false
# - Modify prompt text without code changes
# - Track prompt performance over time